actions.doc:
Check the web content info store and
  • If we have a cache copy of the content and it is fresh enough, then we will return it
  • If we have a cache copy of the content and it is old, then we will rescrape it and cache it
  • If we don't have a cache copy, then we will scrape it and cache it
actions.name: getContent

actions.doc:
Check the web content info store and
  • If we have a cache copy of the content and it is fresh enough, then we will return it
  • If we have a cache copy of the content and it is old, then we will rescrape it and cache it
  • If we don't have a cache copy, then we will scrape it and cache it
The scraping parameters will be taken into account if scraping needs to be done.
